In Major League Baseball, the Kansas City Royals take a 2–1 lead in the 2014 World Series after defeating the San Francisco Giants 3–2 at AT&T Park in San Francisco. (AP via ESPN)In American football, the Baltimore Ravens terminate the contract of running back Ray Rice after videos emerge on the TMZ website of an assault on his then fiancée at the Revel Atlantic City casino. (AP via Seattle Times)